name: 2023 International Conference on Intelligent Control and Computing (IC&C 2023)
content: Paper Publication: All accepted full papers will be published on Conference Publishing Services (CPS), and will be submitted for indexing to ISI/CPCI (Web of Science), Scopus, EI Compendex, Inspec (IET), Google Scholar, CAS, DOAJ, ProQuest, Zentrablatt, EBSCO etc and to the data base of IEEE Xplore.
